.DT
add_message
Disk World creator help
add_message

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
add_message -  This adds a message into the current list of printable messages.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void add_message(string message,
mixed * things)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^message%^RESET%^ - the message to add
%^BOLD%^things%^RESET%^ - the objects which are involved with the message
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/global/events.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This adds a message into the current list of printable messages.  This
will be squided up together and printed out slightly later, this handles
the concatenating of enter messages, and soul messages.  Etc.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
reform_message()

.EP

